                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 139.) I heard a cry of "Stop thief," and saw the prisoner throw the handkerchief down, and run away, after the cry of "Stop thief."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> He knew where I lived; he always knew where to find me.</p>
